(844, 'Baby Taylor Morning Brush', 'A beautiful morning is welcomed by a bright sun. Starting a day without proper dental care is unhygienic. For healthy gums and shining teeth, Taylor too needs to maintain proper oral hygiene. As our little girl is not aware of using brushing accessories, give her guidance for the same. Be with her, when she brushes teeth, massage gums and cleans tongue.', 'https://img.gamemonetize.com/dfdygxkw3o9d0y2hvlw73gy9msk1hwh4/512x384.jpg', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.com/dfdygxkw3o9d0y2hvlw73gy9msk1hwh4/', '', 'Girls', 0, 0),
