(902, 'Find the Girl’s House Key', 'Find the Girl’s House Key is a point and click game developed by 8B Games/Games2Mad Imagine that you had been to a Forest, Unfortunately it’s raining now and you found a girl lost her house key. Here are the interesting puzzles and hidden objects to find the key and go inside. Good luck... Have fun!', 'https://img.gamemonetize.com/fxz3aga24z352b3ia7lm1hflrow5vhex/512x384.jpg', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.com/fxz3aga24z352b3ia7lm1hflrow5vhex/', '', 'Puzzles', 0, 0);
