(1246, 'Nail Salon 3D', 'Nail Salon 3D is a nail art game for all ages. There are a variety of nail polishes in the game for you to choose from. Besides, every time you complete a manicure, you will get the rewards, and the reward can unlock more interesting nail art stickers. Let\'s show your skill!', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ac315891cc6e4c738744eb8071c016a4-512x384.jpeg', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/ac315891cc6e4c738744eb8071c016a4/', '0', 'Arcade', 0, 0);
